MILAN: Inter Milan have signed Manchester United's Belgium striker Romelu Lukaku, the Italian club announced on Thursday, in a deal reported by local media at 80 million euros (73.8 million pounds).
"Inter is not for everyone, that's why I'm here", Lukaku, who was wearing the Inter kit, said in a video posted on the Serie A club's official Twitter feed.
(Reporting by Rohith Nair in Bengaluru; editing by Ken Ferris)